":"1324 kJ \/ 317 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving plate, frying pan, non-stick pan, hob","hintsAndTricks":["The celeriac can be steamed ahead, then floured, egged and breadcrumbed before frying and serving."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","1h","4 portions"]}